OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost likely
OL,6,Fdry with often large amounts of high
OL,7,Fcloud, although there is a small
OL,8,Fchance of thunderstorms just brushing
OL,9,Fsouthern Kent as they move across the
OL,10,FEnglish Channel.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FGenerally dry and fine, with
OL,13,Fjust a small chance of isolated
OL,14,Fthunderstorms developing. Temperatures
OL,15,Fclimbing, becoming hot and humid
OL,16,Falthough onshore breezes will keep
OL,17,Fsome coastal areas cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
