OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FPredominantly dry and becoming hot or
OL,7,Fvery hot, with the heat peaking
OL,8,FTuesday. Humid and very warm nights.
OL,9,FChance of occasional low cloud along
OL,10,Fthe coasts, and isolated thunderstorms
OL,11,FMonday.
